The '''Ratawi oil field''' is an [[oil field]] located in [[Basra Governorate]]. It was discovered in 1950 and developed by [[Basrah Oil Company]]. It will begin production in 2018 and will produce [[oil]]. The total [[proven reserves]] of the Ratawi oil field are around {{convert|10|e9oilbbl}}, and production will be centered on {{convert|250000|oilbbl/d|m3/d}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crescentpetroleum.com/html/iraq_projects.html|title=Ratawi oil-field in Southern Iraq|year=2013|publisher=crescentpetroleum.com|accessdate=2014-04-26}}</ref>

